title: Plackers Micro Mint Dental Flossers, Travel Pack, Perfect Travel Size, Easy Storage, Dental Care On-The-Go, Fresh Mint Flavor, 12 Count
description: You've got smiles for miles. Keep it looking fresh with Plackers Micro Mint Flossers. Easily remove food particles with smooth Super Tufffloss, engineered not to stretch, shred or break and with a built-in fold-out toothpick that folds away after use. The easy grip handle provides more control and comfort while cleaning between your teeth and gums. Rely on Plackers to Get the Gunk Out. Enjoy fresh breath with delicious mint flavor that leaves your mouth with a fresh clean feeling. These flossers come in convenient, on-the-go packs and are perfect for travel. Includes 12 mint dental flossers. Smile Like Everyone's Watching!
top_review: I bought 2 of these, one for the car, and one for my toiletries bag for when I travel.The actual plackers are the normal ones, which are good enough.Pros:- Portable Travel Case: In all honesty, the only reason I bought these (I typically buy the massive packs from Costco, and refill the travel cases)- Compact Size: The compact size of the travel case makes it easy to slip into even small pockets or compartments. It's perfect for travel or everyday use, providing a discreet and convenient way to carry dental floss picks wherever I go.- Effective Flossing: The dental floss picks themselves are highly effective at removing food particles and debris from between teeth. The mint flavor leaves my mouth feeling fresh and clean, making it a pleasant experience to floss on a regular basis.- Durable Construction: Despite their small size, these floss picks are sturdy and well-made. I've never had one break or fray during use, ensuring a hassle-free flossing experience every time.Cons:- Case-Dependent Value: While the floss picks themselves are effective and of good quality, the value of this product is mainly derived from the inclusion of the travel case. If you don't need the case, you may find other floss picks to be more cost-effective.In summary, if you're in need of a convenient and portable solution for flossing on-the-go, look no further than Plackers Micro Mint Dental Floss Picks with Travel Case. With their effective flossing action, durable construction, and added convenience of the travel case, they're a must-have for anyone who prioritizes oral hygiene while traveling or out and about.Highly recommended!

title: Garnier Micellar Cleansing Water, All-in-1 Makeup Remover and Facial Cleanser, For All Skin Types, 3.4 Fl Oz (100mL), 1 Count (Packaging May Vary)
description: This All-in-1 Micellar Cleansing Water is surprisingly powerful yet gentle to skin. It effectively removes makeup, cleanses and refreshes skin. A multi-purpose cleanser that contains Micellar technology. Like a magnet, micelles capture and lift away dirt, oil and makeup without harsh rubbing, leaving skin perfectly clean, hydrated and refreshed without over-drying. â€¢ All-in-1 cleanser and makeup remover cleanses, removes makeup and refreshes skin â€¢ Oil-Free, Alcohol-Free, Fragrance-Free â€¢ Micelle Technology attracts dirt, oil and makeup like a magnet without harsh rubbing â€¢ All skin types, even sensitive TO REMOVE EYE MAKEUP: Hold pad over closed eyes for a few seconds, then gently wipe without harsh rubbing. TO CLEAN SKIN & REMOVE FACE MAKEUP: Gently wipe all over until skin is completely clean from makeup and impurities. Use daily, AM/PM. No need to rinse. Avoid contact with eyes. If contact occurs, rinse thoroughly with water.
top_review: This Garnier micellar water is absolutely fantastic! It removes makeup effortlessly without any harsh rubbing or tugging on delicate eye area skin. Even waterproof mascara comes off easily with just a gentle press of the cotton pad - no more scrubbing that irritates my eyes.The formula is perfectly gentle for sensitive skin while still being powerful enough to remove every trace of makeup and daily grime. It doesn't leave any greasy residue or require rinsing, making it perfect for quick cleansing or travel situations when water isn't convenient.What impressed me most is how hydrating it feels - my skin actually feels softer and more moisturized after cleansing instead of tight and stripped like with some harsh cleansers. The vegan formula gives me confidence that it's made with quality, ethical ingredients.Perfect for lazy nights when you want clean skin without a full skincare routine, or as the first step in double cleansing. Works beautifully on face and eyes with no stinging or irritation. One bottle lasts surprisingly long even with daily use.Essential for anyone wanting effective, gentle makeup removal. This has completely simplified my evening routine while delivering better results than more expensive alternatives.Outstanding gentle cleansing - highly recommend for sensitive, effective skincare!

title: Dramamine Motion Sickness Less Drowsy, Travel Vial, Multicolor, 8 Count
description: Dramamine All Day Less Drowsy Motion Sickness Relief prevents and treats motion sickness, nausea, vomiting and dizziness for up to 24 hours. The tablets come in a convenient, safety Travel Vial for anytime motion sickness symptoms strike. Get less drowsy relief from motion sickness when you need it most from the number 1 pharmacist-recommended brand!* Wherever your adventure takes you, Dramamine is a vacation essential in your travel medicine bag. Don't let motion sickness affect your plans on your next cruise, theme park, visit or road trip. Dramamine fits with your other travel size toiletries and travel must haves. If you know you are going on an adventure that is likely to cause motion sickness and nausea, take Dramamine Less Drowsy BEFORE the trek. Also, be sure to drink plenty of water and avoid alcohol, which can increase dehydration and nausea. Take Dramamine and Take Control. For adults and children 6 and older. See packaging for dosing instructions and warnings. *Named by Pharmacy Times and U.S. News & World Report as number 1 Pharmacist-Recommended Brand for 2022 Motion Sickness Remedies Category.
categories: ["Health & Household","Health Care","Over-the-Counter Medication","Digestion & Nausea","Motion Sickness & Nausea"]
top_review: Pair of noise cancelling headphones and this almost zero drowsy version of Dramamine is how I love my flights to Japan now. The normal Dramamine makes me so groggy that I had to rent a place to sleep after arriving to Japan and the entire trip I felt like an uneasy zombie. If you get motion sickness, this is it as it's super effective in "calming" all your nerves. The dose is perfect and not too strong. It works relatively quickly about 1 hour before the flight.No smells, easy swallow capsules, very easy to dose and go! Highly recommended!

The product receives positive feedback for its gentle formula that doesn't irritate sensitive skin, and one customer notes it's gentle enough to use multiple times a day. While some customers say it's worth every penny, others find it overpriced. The smell receives mixed reactions, with some customers noting it has no distinct smell while others compare it to bleach.
